                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pour Nisami quittant Shakspeare,\nIl se parfuma de çantal,\nEt sur un mètre oriental\nNota le chant qu'Hudhud soupire."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Comme Gœthe sur son divan",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "A Weimar s'isolait des choses",
